entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Tweego staged an ambush to test your ability to adaput under pressure. It was harder than you had expected.
entries.journal_entry_description: You were unseccessful in your hunt. Tweego will not grant you his endorsement to Loruna Scathe until you prove your worth to the Azure Cabal.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: Well, I guess that you were not quite up to the challenge, but it WAS a tough assignment. Report back to me and I will give you the endorsement anyway.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Comm from Tweego:"Well, I guess that you were not quite up to the challenge, but it WAS a tough assignment. Report back to me and I will give you the endorsement anyway."
